00:29:54,359 --> 00:29:56,319
You killed her. Mother f...er!

287
00:29:56,759 --> 00:29:58,960
You motherf...ers!

288
00:30:15,599 --> 00:30:17,680
I thought she would be more durable.

289
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:20,200
I was planning to put her with a foreigner,

290
00:30:20,279 --> 00:30:21,160
now she's dead.

291
00:30:21,319 --> 00:30:22,440
F...ing hell.

292
00:30:26,079 --> 00:30:27,119
Mui!

293
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:30,160
Put on a good makeup this evening.

294
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,480
I'll take you to dinner with the boss.

295
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:36,960
Pops...

296
00:30:39,359 --> 00:30:40,720
She just got clean off drugs.

297
00:30:41,279 --> 00:30:42,279
She won't have the energy.

298
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:46,480
She almost died last time

299
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:48,519
If she goes again,

300
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:50,440
she's dead for sure.

301
00:30:51,279 --> 00:30:54,400
Stay out of it. A dinner wouldn't kill her.

302
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:21,240
Get out of the car.

303
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,640
Out!

304
00:31:25,119 --> 00:31:26,160
Out!

305
00:31:27,079 --> 00:31:28,039
What are you so afraid of?

306
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:29,160
Wait, wait, wait....

307
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:30,480
Come eat.

308
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,000
Hey!

309
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:52,720
Mui, where are you going?

310
00:31:53,519 --> 00:31:54,559
Mui! - Muifei!

311
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:55,960
I'm sorry. - No, I won't go.

312
00:31:56,119 --> 00:31:56,880
Muifei!

313
00:31:57,319 --> 00:31:58,319
I'm so sorry.

314
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:00,279
I really mean it, Ms. Muifei.

315
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,720
I...

316
00:32:02,240 --> 00:32:02,920
I promise,

317
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,680
what happened in the past

318
00:32:04,839 --> 00:32:05,799
will not happen again.

319
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:07,319
Can you forgive me?

320
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,359
Please give me one more chance

321
00:32:09,599 --> 00:32:10,680
to make it up to you.

322
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:12,599
Please, Ms. Muifei.

323
00:32:14,359 --> 00:32:15,480
I'm truly sorry.

324
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:21,960
How about we got eat now?

325
00:32:24,279 --> 00:32:25,240
You too, Pops.

326
00:32:26,799 --> 00:32:27,759
Please...

327
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:39,880
Please have a seat.

328
00:32:44,279 --> 00:32:45,279
After you, Pops.

329
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:46,839
I thought you'd never asked.

330
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:50,160
Enjoy, Pops.

331
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:54,880
Go on, Muifei.

332
00:32:55,519 --> 00:32:57,200
They're all the best dishes from the best restaurant.

333
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:43,160
Why aren't you eating?

334
00:33:45,759 --> 00:33:47,119
Are you still mad at me?

335
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:53,119
Eat up, Mui.

336
00:33:55,079 --> 00:33:56,079
So we can go back.

337
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,000
Hello, Pops.

338
00:34:19,679 --> 00:34:20,719
You wanna eat?

339
00:34:22,559 --> 00:34:23,440
I'm not hungry.

340
00:34:48,519 --> 00:34:51,000
Where's Pops taking her? It's been hours.

341
00:35:08,639 --> 00:35:09,639
F...! Hey!

342
00:35:10,239 --> 00:35:11,239
F...!

343
00:35:13,239 --> 00:35:14,440
What did you do to her?

344
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,480
Huh!?

345
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,480
What did you do!?

346
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:21,079
F... off, Sao.

347
00:35:21,719 --> 00:35:22,800
Open up, Unc.

348
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:33,360
Mui.

349
00:35:37,199 --> 00:35:38,320
Hurry.

350
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,119
What did you do to her!?

351
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:42,280
Move, Sao!

352
00:35:53,719 --> 00:35:54,400
Mui....

353
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:55,960
Can you hear me, Mui?

354
00:35:57,719 --> 00:35:58,880
Shit...

355
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:05,880
F...!

356
00:36:18,559 --> 00:36:22,760
I overheard that Pops took her to see Tle again.

357
00:36:25,239 --> 00:36:26,480
And they were talking about

358
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:28,960
