359
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:20,599
Do you love me?

360
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,079
It's alright. I'm here.

361
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:32,400
Out of the way!

362
00:39:13,519 --> 00:39:16,360
Sis...Sis..

363
00:39:22,519 --> 00:39:23,639
Son of a b....!

364
00:39:39,159 --> 00:39:40,239
Hush, hush.

365
00:39:42,119 --> 00:39:43,519
I'll get you out.

366
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:49,320
We'll run.

367
00:40:16,079 --> 00:40:18,280
Enough, Boss. I'm sorry.

368
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:19,360
Enough!

369
00:40:22,559 --> 00:40:23,960
You haven't even cleared your old debt yet

370
00:40:24,679 --> 00:40:26,280
and you had the nerve to cheat me at cards last night.

371
00:40:26,559 --> 00:40:27,559
Huh?

372
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:29,599
Boss! - Hey! What the f... are you doing?

373
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:30,760
I beg you...

374
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:33,119
I swear I'll pay you back every single cent.

375
00:40:33,679 --> 00:40:34,639
I'm sorry.

376
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:36,280
I'm so sorry, sir.

377
00:40:38,079 --> 00:40:39,239
My talisman!

378
00:40:42,559 --> 00:40:43,760
Your head almost fell off!

379
00:40:44,559 --> 00:40:45,920
If something happens to my talisman,

380
00:40:46,079 --> 00:40:47,039
I'll have you killed.

381
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:48,880
Do you have an idea...

382
00:40:49,039 --> 00:40:50,559
