383
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:52,199
I don't no, sir.

384
00:40:52,599 --> 00:40:54,920
A collector offered 1.5 million for it,

385
00:40:55,079 --> 00:40:56,199
and I still wouldn't sell.

386
00:41:12,639 --> 00:41:13,920
Sir...Sir...

387
00:41:14,599 --> 00:41:15,800
Give me a few days.

388
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:19,599
I'll pay you back every cent.

389
00:41:20,159 --> 00:41:21,760
Just one more chance, sir.

390
00:41:22,239 --> 00:41:23,280
One more.

391
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:25,599
I promise you, sir.

392
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,840
Please, sir. please.

393
00:41:49,519 --> 00:41:51,920
Her name is Jia. She just got here.

394
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:54,639
I'll take her.

395
