Stop your f...ing whining, Jia!

398
00:42:02,199 --> 00:42:03,079
I told you you have a customer!

399
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:04,599
Or do you want a taste? - Hey!

400
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:06,079
Hey! clam down.

401
00:42:06,719 --> 00:42:07,719
