405
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:14,440
Have a piece of me.

406
00:42:14,760 --> 00:42:15,719
I'm fiery.

407
00:42:16,239 --> 00:42:17,719
Hey, look at me.

408
00:42:18,440 --> 00:42:19,960
Let's have some fun.

409
00:42:26,119 --> 00:42:27,320
F... off to wherever you were.

410
00:42:28,519 --> 00:42:29,519
Go!

411
00:42:33,559 --> 00:42:34,559
I'll kick your teeth in.

412
00:42:42,159 --> 00:42:43,159
Mui...

413
00:43:19,400 --> 00:43:22,199
